### 1. Check IP is valid
GET https://kong.staging.rnd.ukfast/safedns/v1/records?name=89.163.37.46.in-addr.arpa
Accept: */*
Cache-Control: no-cache
Authorization: myukfast
Content-Type:  application/json

> {%
